The Postmaster of Mafdet holds an open commission for a complete navigation survey of the Khardaan necropolis. The ancient burial complex and surrounding dune approaches lack current comprehensive documentation in the harbor authority's reference files, creating navigation gaps for expeditions operating in the area. Survey every accessible tomb approach, dune crossing, and interior section of the necropolis and return with a complete route record.
Your Khardaan necropolis survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority. The completed navigation record is now the primary reference for expeditions operating at Khardaan, and the postmaster has closed the open commission.
